    "Name": "Bishamon",
    "Details": "Engineers had clearly intended for the BSN-3K to engage its enemies at short to medium ranges. The primary weapon on the 'Mech is a MRM-20 launcher, backed up by a pair of ER Medium Lasers and two highly accurate Medium Pulse Lasers. While the 'Mech is vulnerable to long-range attacks, when engaged in close quarters the Bishamon is an extremely dangerous 'Mech to face.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Quad Mech</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.03</color></b>",
